WORKDIR /FGO-py
#&& python3.9 -m pip config set global.index-url https://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/ \

 && pip uninstall -y opencv-contrib-python \
 && pip install --no-cache-dir opencv-contrib-python-headless \
 && rm -r ~/.cache/pip
CMD python fgo.py cli
